OL,3,C'I work endlessly and get nowhere -
OL,4,Csometimes I can't afford to shower'
OL,6,FA young business owner has been left
OL,7,Ffeeling depressed and suicidal as she
OL,8,Fstruggles to make ends meet.
OL,10,FChloe says she feels "forever stuck"
OL,11,Fin a world where money is "always an
OL,12,Fissue".
OL,14,FThe 26-year-old from Bristol grew up
OL,15,Fin foster care and says this has made
OL,16,Fher journey to becoming a business
OL,17,Fowner more difficult than most.
