OL,3,C'I work endlessly and get nowhere -
OL,4,Csometimes I can't afford to shower'
OL,6,F"I can't even begin to express how
OL,7,Fhard it's been," she told ITV News. "I
OL,8,Fwish there were more financial
OL,9,Fopportunities for people in my
OL,10,Fsituation."
OL,12,FBut even with her own business, the
OL,13,Fcost of living crisis is putting an
OL,14,Fimmense strain on Chloe.
OL,16,FShe said: "I work endlessly and I feel
OL,17,Flike I get nowhere. Money is always an
OL,18,Fissue - I feel like I'm forever stuck
OL,19,Fin this place.
