OL,3,C'I work endlessly and get nowhere -
OL,4,Csometimes I can't afford to shower'
OL,6,F"I feel like it's impossible to save
OL,7,Fmoney because bills are constantly
OL,8,Fgoing up due to inflation."
OL,10,FRising bills mean Chloe often has to
OL,11,Fgo without essentials - including food.
OL,13,F"As soon as my money comes in, I buy
OL,14,Fall of my food, my shower essentials
OL,15,Fand stuff like that. Then I focus on
OL,16,Fmy bills. I don't have much left at
OL,17,Fthe end of it because it all adds up.
