OL,3,C'I work endlessly and get nowhere -
OL,4,Csometimes I can't afford to shower'
OL,6,F"I sacrifice essentials like meals and
OL,7,Fsometimes I don't have enough money to
OL,8,Fhave a shower. I feel like I'm getting
OL,9,Fto a point now where it's make or
OL,10,Fbreak."
OL,12,FShe said it has left her feeling
OL,13,Fsuicidal, adding: "It feels like a
OL,14,Fdownward spiral and I'm struggling to
OL,15,Fget myself out of it because of my
OL,16,Fsupport network, which seems to be non-
OL,17,Fexistent. I need someone to put their
OL,18,Fhand in and pull me out. But that's
OL,19,Fnot available to me so it just makes
OL,20,Fme very depressed."
