OL,3,C'I work endlessly and get nowhere -
OL,4,Csometimes I can't afford to shower'
OL,6,FShe said she wishes there was more
OL,7,Ffinancial support for care leavers,
OL,8,Fadding: "Something that I recognise,
OL,9,Fbeing a person that's experienced
OL,10,Ffoster care since I was very young, is
OL,11,Fthat we get pushed into this
OL,12,Fstereotypical category of being
OL,13,Fincapable or a trouble-maker or
OL,14,Fsomething like that. When actually, we
OL,15,Fdon't have support.
OL,17,F"That's why it's important to
OL,18,Fprioritise people in this situation."
